<html>
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/main/resources/css/employee/popup.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="popup" id="popup">
    <div class="popup_body">
        <div class="popup_content">
            <a href="#" class="popup_close"><img src="https://img.icons8.com/material-sharp/24/fa314a/close-window.png"/></a>
            <div class="popup_text">
                <p>This page displays all of your active orders. Each order has buttons for control.</p>
                <br>
                <p>Help about aim:</p>
                <p>NEW - means that the purpose of the order is to connect a new service</p>
                <p>DISCONNECT - means that the purpose of the order is to deactivate the service</p>
                <p>SUSPEND - means that the purpose of the order is to suspend the service</p>
                <br>
                <p>Help about status:</p>
                <p>ENTERING - means that the order has been created in the system, but an employee has not yet been assigned to it.</p>
                <p>IN PROGRESS - means that an employee has been assigned to the order and it is already being executed</p>
                <p>SUSPENDED - means that the order is suspended due to technical reasons</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
